description: 作为一个富有爱心且懂得感恩的主人，这款以宠物照片为设计原型，用可雕塑软陶土手工制作并涂色的定制化小雕像，能让你为每一个曾经陪伴过你的爱宠打造一枚栩栩如生并可永远珍藏的纪念品

content: Instantly fill your bland room with incredible color by flicking on this rainbow light projecting lamp. With this diy lamp, you’ll get to design and paint a colorful and abstract work of art that will be reflected onto the walls and ceiling.

content: Give your dining room a striking appearance by creating some relaxing ambient lighting with this LED light river table. This sleek canary wood table comes fitted with built-in LEDs that you can set to a range of vibrant colors to match your dining room’s decor.

content: Earth’s mightiest hero is here to rescue you from the darkness in the form of this Dragon Ball Z spirit bomb cloud lamp. Goku’s massive spirit bomb orb is outfitted with over 50 customizable LEDs that change color while displaying a kickass laser show over the cloud.

description: 如果你和你的灵魂伴侣恰好都是星战系列的狂热粉丝，那大可尝试一下这款以死星为主题设计独特且有银色和金色两种外观可选的订婚戒指，让那颗镶嵌在死星上的宝石或钻戒见证你们彼此的相爱相知

Accelerate the aging process by turning your adorable tot into an old little spinster using these grandma baby costumes. The costumes include a set of glasses with a chain holder and a darling hat that you can combine with any outfit to create a unique look.

content: Stand out above everyone else at the club by strutting your stuff in this stunning neon UV glow worm dress. This groovy dress features a psychedelic styled design that comes to life under a black light – giving it an insanely provocative glow.

content: Who better to join you for a delicious snack of cookies and milk than the Cookie Monster? The Cookie Monster coffee mug’s creative design lets you place a couple of cookies inside his mouth for safekeeping as they wait to be dipped in the milk above.

Add some color and personality to your backyard or patio by placing a lively arrangement on this outdoor oak shaped tree shelf. Each sturdy wooden branch of this cleverly designed shelf makes the ideal home for a small little potted plant.

content: Give the Star Wars fanatic in your life a smile from ear to ear by surprising them with this hand carved wooden Millennium Falcon. This impressive replica of the iconic spacecraft has been expertly hand carved from a solid piece of wood.

description: 这款极具创意的趣味产品从浩瀚的艺术史和流行网红文化中精心选取了辨识度极高的人物或风景，并以此为题材再加工为风格独特的蚀刻素描版本，是送给所有自诩对艺术颇有鉴赏品味的技术控最好的礼物
content: Give your art collection some 21st century appeal by adding one of these famous art Etch-A-Sketch’s to your collection. Etsy store PrincessEtch specializes in immortalizing some of pop culture’s most recognizable figures, paintings, and characters on Etch-A-Sketch’s!

content: Pay homage to the scariest show from your childhood by rocking this awesome “Are You Afraid Of The Dark?” pin. This small and nostalgic accessory displays the starting sequence of the iconic Nickelodeon show playing on an old school box television set.

This Spider-Man mask with moveable eyes will give your Web-Slinger ensemble an authentic feel that will turn heads. The eyes on this Spidey mask are designed to open and close – giving the costume an unprecedentedly realistic appearance.

Bring a piece of the Early Jurassic period into the twenty-first century by adding this life size Dilophosaurus replica to your collection. This masterfully hand made replica captures the terrifying Dilophosaurus in his iconic attack pose.

Pay homage to your favorite mutant by storing your razor sharp cutlery in this Wolverine claws steak knife holder. The closed fist design gives the impression that your steak knives are actually Wolverine’s indestructible Adamantium claws.

Etsy shop Diegator Engineering creates incredible sci-fi inspired cosplay helmets that are perfect for any futuristic costume. This incredibly well built helmet can automatically close and open at the push of a button and is accented by a large glowing central LED.

If traditional shiny gold and silver bands aren’t your thing, feast your eyes on this men’s rustic wedding band. This elegant and understated band is made from a hammered sterling silver ring complemented by a 14K gold streak that extends all the way around.

Ensure you make a splash at Comic-Con by showing up dressed in this eye-catching tactical cyberpunk body armor. Skillfully handcrafted from EVA foam, neoprene, and plastic, this futuristic getup includes torso/shoulder armor, arm braces, and a light up LED helmet.

The One With All The Cards is the aptly named Friends themed Cards Against Humanity styled game that is perfect for any fan of the famed TV sitcom. Each card in this entertaining game comes filled with hilarious references from the iconic TV series.

Keep your poultry warm and cozy when the temperature dips by slipping her into a chicken turtleneck sweater. This machine washable garment is hand-crocheted using 100% cotton yarn and can be customized to ensure a perfect fit.

Add a bit of natural beauty to your bedroom’s landscape by turning on this mushrooms night light. Each of the little mushrooms sprouting up form the wooden log shaped base comes embedded with a small LED that gives off a soothing and gentle glow.

Fire off a couple rounds of your favorite alcoholic beverage after chilling them with these whiskey cooling bullets. Once chilled in the freezer, these stainless steel ice cube alternatives are placed in the drink to keep it icy cold without watering it down.

Nothing says true love like pizza. Let everyone know how much you love your little bundle of joy with these father and son matching pizza shirts. Each shirt is made from premium cotton with a lively colorful design that won’t fade after the first wash.

Nurture your artistic side while under Mary Jane’s intoxicating spell by sitting down with the coloring book for stoners. This psychedelic coloring book features over 25 intricate designs and groovy looking creatures that you can bring to life using crayons and markers.

Experience heaven on earth by biting into one of the delectable caramel bacon brownies. Each gooey and chocolaty brownie comes bathed in a thick coat of caramel and is then topped off with crispy fried bacon bits.

Commemorate your favorite program for crappy art with this cute little MS Paint enamel pin. This handmade metal alloy gem measures 3″ x 2.6″ and perfectly recreates the simplistic user interface of the iconic Microsoft Paint program.

Keep your energetic tot from turning your home upside down by entertaining him with this busy box baby activity center. Each face of this fun cube comes littered with a slew of fun little actives designed to entertain and help with the development of your toddler.

Give your bedroom a bit of A-list Hollywood flair with this stunning Nicolas Cage sequin pillow. With an effortless stroke of your hand along its surface, the eye-catching shimmering sequin design will give way to an image of the one true God’s flawless face.

Decorate your home with the greatest literary works of the English language with the classic book staircase stickers. These unique decals transform any dull staircase into a seemingly endless pile of classic books conveniently stacked so you can get to the second floor.

Fight against the ravages of time by keeping your skin feeling clean and rejuvenated when you wash yourself with this Fountain of Youth soap. This vegan-friendly artisan soap is handmade with nurturing ingredients that will leave your skin feeling smooth and squeaky clean.

titleEN: A Bunch Of Dogs In Here Doormat
content: Kindly and humorously warn unsuspecting guests of the madness that awaits them inside your home with this “there’s, like, a bunch of dogs in here” doormat. This handmade doormat measures 30 x 18 inches and is ideal for either outdoor or indoor use.

Turn your home into the talk of the neighborhood by proudly displaying this recycled metal Megatron. This jaw-dropping work of art masterfully brings the dreaded Deceptacon leader Megatron to life using a mix of recycled metal with old car and motorcycle parts.

Make your Link cosplay as authentic as possible by getting your hands on this Zelda Guardian Sword. This 3D printed 34.6″ long LED Guardian Sword comes with a micro USB port for easy recharging and has a battery life of six continuous hours.

Behold, the internet! This once in a lifetime offer from the Elders of the Internet gives you the opportunity to own the internet – yes, the whole internet! The internet is weightless and wireless, and has been de-magnetized by none other than Stephen Hawking.

Awe and shock your guests next time you invite them over for drinks by sipping your beverage from this incredible human skull goblet. Each macabre goblet is masterfully hand sculpted from food grade materials and can hold up to 16 ounces of your favorite beverage.

Stand out from the bunch at the next Comic-Con you attend by arming yourself with this striking lightsaber katana blade. This handmade Star Wars inspired prop measures 27.5 inches long and is skillfully crafted from a clear acrylic sheet that comes to life when lit.

Beef up your home’s security with the greatest weapons in history by purchasing this Acme weapons crate. This sizable crate comes filled with a range of deadly weapons like a two-handed machete, a mace, a bullwhip, and a tomahawk among others.

Rock the tattooed look without having to endure hours of pain by slipping into these dazzling tattoo tights. Each of these striking tights is made from a breathable and soft yet durable fabric that’s machine washable and comes decorated with a custom hand painted tattoo-like design.

Show your dear friends that you love them – in your own special way – using these hilarious anti-greeting cards. Instead of mushy love poems, these cards feature in-your-face graphics along with equally bold heart-warming messages.

Get Mr. Fluffums ready for combat by suiting him up in this cat battle armor. This custom leather armor is flexible enough for your cat to move freely without hampering its agility and looks glorious on any breed of cat. The neighborhood dog won’t stand a chance.

Experience the ultimate power in the universe by crafting your own Infinity Gauntlet using this DIY crochet guide. This PDF includes step-by-step instructions on how to make a detailed version of Thanos’s iconic weapon – ideal for the comic book fanatic in your life.

Experience the perfect blend of magic and sweetness by sprinkling your food with some magical unicorn sugar. This unique turbinado sugar blend combines blueberry, hibiscus, and lemon sugars into a sweet and colorful combination ideal for topping off any dessert.

Make your loyalties known to everyone who enters your home and lays eyes on this metal Darth Vader statue. This out-of-this-world masterpiece is skillfully handcrafted from recycled metal and old auto parts to create a menacing structure that stands 8.2 feet tall.

Everything tastes better with a little sprinkle of bacon on it! This one of a kind seasoning captures the sweet, smoky bacon flavor we all know and love, and adds just a hint of heat at the end for a truly unique taste to whatever you throw it on.

There’s no better way for a racing enthusiast to start their day than by checking the time on one of these speedometer clocks. Each clock in the collection is an accurate handmade recreation of the speedometer of a classic automobile.

Show off your love of firearms by hanging up the bullet clock in your humble abode. This custom handmade piece features an eye-catching display where the hours are marked with .223 dummy rounds and the minutes are marked with 9mm dummy rounds.

Put a smile on your favorite teacher’s face by showing them some appreciation with one of these personalized face stamps. The photo that you submit gets made into a unique rubber stamp displaying the person’s face and custom text of your choosing.

Make your home a more interesting place for visitors with this tentacle wall sculpture. This masterfully handmade urethane resin and aluminum sculpture measures 24 inches and features an eye-catching turquoise hue that’ll pop in any room.

Keep your relationship fun and exciting with activities from this date ideas personalized jar. Each little jar comes with a quaint custom label displaying the couple’s names and is filled with 15 tokens – each with a date idea for you and your sweetie to enjoy together.

Help get more in tune with nature by installing the tree root chandelier in your home. The chandelier’s unique design makes it seem as if a light bulb studded tree is growing out of the ceiling and conveniently illuminating the room below – making it ideal for nature lovers.

Transform yourself into a fierce futuristic warrior by slipping into this cyber gladiator armor. This durable and functional handmade armor allows for smooth bending of the joints and comes with an integrated light that can be customized with the color of your choice.

Level up your living room’s interior decor with this stunning retro NES controller coffee table. The top of the table features a professionally printed vinyl decal styled like the iconic rectangular grey, black, and red controllers of the NES.

Bring back an internet classic by dressing up in this Nyan Cat onesie. This spectacularly multi-colored ensemble captures the essence of the classic internet meme with a bright pink base complemented by glorious rainbow accents on the arms and legs.

Add a macabre touch to any part of your humble abode by placing this trapped ghost in a can on display. Each steel can comes stuffed with a real life ghost along with a custom label indicating the date and location where the ghost was captured.

Make your room look heavenly with these light up cloud lamps! Easy to install, these ethereal cloud lamps are made using a hypoallergenic material that make them ideal for the nursery and come with eight unique lighting modes for added flair.

Experience cuteness overload on a daily basis by complementing your outfit with this mini sloth felt jewelry. Handmade from 100% wool, this adorable little three-toed sloth gently hangs on a soft leatherette necklace to keep you company all day long.

titleEN: Out Of Character Star Wars Prints
content: See your favorite intergalactic personalities like never before by gazing at these out of character Star Wars prints. Each print measures 12″ x 16″ and depicts iconic characters like Darth Vader, Boba Fett, and C-3PO lounging in flower filled meadows.

Add some personality to your humble abode by laying out this wine/work door mat. The humorous and simple design of this 30 x 18 inch handmade coir mat comes with helpful symbols that show you which way leads to work and which way leads to your precious wine.

Sleep more soundly than ever by slipping on this aromatherapy lavender sleep mask before you hit the hay. It features a flower outer fabric, a 100% unbleached cotton face-side fabric, and is filled with organic lavender flowers that’ll relax you and help you stay sound asleep.

Ponder the meaning of life and wash your hands at the same time with these human fetus soap bars. Each one of these strange and eerie soap bars are made using a synthetic fetus mold, goat’s milk soap, and lavender oil for a fresh aroma and moisturizing feeling.

titleEN: Doctor Strange Light Up LED Spell Disc
content: Wow everyone with your sorcery by arming yourself with this handmade Doctor Strange light up LED spell disc. The disc comes with 45 ultra bright LEDs that can be wirelessly controlled using a discreet control that creates the illusion you’re altering the disc’s color using magic.

Send your taste buds into ecstasy by sinking your teeth into these chocolate covered bacon strips. Each delicious and crispy bacon strip is dipped in rich milk chocolate that creates a truly savory sweet and salty flavor that’s hard to beat.

Get an up close and personal view into the cramped living quarters of captured Pokemon by adding this replica Pokeball display jar to your growing collection. The Pokeball is skillfully hand crafted to be as lifelike as possible.

Make your baby’s gender reveal the most exciting event to hit your town with the burnout gender reveal kit. You simply attach the pack to any one of your car’s tires, peel out, and watch as the air is filled with a cloud of smoke signaling the sex of your unborn baby.

Keep shredding long after the sun goes down by outfitting your board with this LED snowboard lighting kit. The kit comes with over 16 feet of high quality battery powered LED strips that you can set to dozens of color combinations using a handy remote.

Give your bedroom a lovely and inviting post-apocalyptic glow by switching on this nuclear explosion lamp. This eye-catching light fixture depicts the gigantic menacing mushroom cloud that forms following the explosion of a nuclear bomb.

Ensure you’re as comfortable as possible during your next soak by placing all your bathtime essentials on this relaxation wooden bathtub caddy. Each handmade caddy has a wine glass holder, two recessed holes for tea lights, and a slot large enough for your tablet.

Let your aquatic friends reach new heights by placing this floating fish observatory in your pond. This Plexiglas aquarium floats independently, comes with an anchor to keep it in place, and gives you an up-close look at your fishy residents.

Ensure you always have a small piece of your loved one with you by getting your very own personalized handwriting bracelet. Each piece is customized with a sterling silver pendant displaying the signature of your choice.

Add some variety to your garden in the form of vibrant little succulents by planting these mixed succulent plant seeds. With some tender love and care you’ll be able to grow a variety of small rare succulents of all shapes and colors.

Treat your eyes to a flurry of radiant colors by gazing at this peacock ore iridescent rock. These gorgeous eye-catching stones range in size from approximately 1 to 1.5 inches long and each display a myriad of incredibly vivid blue and purple hues.

Turn heads at next year’s BlizzCon by becoming the living embodiment of the robed terrorist known only as the Reaper. It’s masterfully crafted from polyurethane plastic and EVA to facilitate movement and hand painted with game-accurate details.

Become the living embodiment of the most merciless and pitiless cyborg race in the universe by climbing inside this fully operational steampunk Dalek. This geeky masterpiece can travel at 6mph and is controlled via cameras connected to internal display screens.

Give your co-workers a piece of your mind when they try and pester you in the mornings using this anti-morning person coffee mug. The mug has an 11 ounce capacity and features lettering printed using dye sublimation to prevent it from fading over time.

Give your game room a real arcade feel using these mini replica pinball machines. While these 1/12th scale pinball machines may be too small to actually play, these handmade items come intricately designed with a geeky motif ideal for adding some style to your room.
